wdi-BX.GSR.FCTY.CD.def: Primary income receipts refer to employee compensation paid to resident workers working abroad and investment income (receipts on direct investment, portfolio investment, other investments, and receipts on reserve assets). Data are in current U.S. dollars.
wdi-BX.GSR.FCTY.CD.name: Primary income receipts
wdi-BX.GSR.FCTY.CD.source: International Monetary Fund, Balance of Payments Statistics Yearbook and data files.
